Source: pgmemento
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/pgMemento/pgMemento

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pgmemento
Architecture: all
Provides: postgresql-pgmemento
Depends: postgresql-PGVERSION, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Transaction-based audit trail and schema versioning for PostgreSQL PGVERSION
 pgMemento provides row auditing, DDL tracking, schema versioning, and
 restoration helpers implemented entirely in PL/pgSQL.
